Class Column

java.lang.Object
org.hibernate.mapping.Column
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Cloneable, Selectable, ColumnTypeInformation
Direct Known Subclasses:
AggregateColumn
public sealed class Column extends Object implements Selectable, Serializable, Cloneable, ColumnTypeInformation permits AggregateColumn
A mapping model object representing a column of a relational database table.
